  "detailed_description": "From Soil to Bottle is a sandbox winemaking simulator that blends cozy charm with unparalleled realism. In this captivating game, you'll immerse yourself in the art and science of winemaking, where every decision shapes the character and quality of your wines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/f4c0089b4f13296ac8dbf5d65d2f80df.webp?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=59 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/b611703413f869a8d18a5bd75dd71c45.poster.avif?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/b611703413f869a8d18a5bd75dd71c45.webm?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/b611703413f869a8d18a5bd75dd71c45.mp4?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Delve into the intricate details of viticulture and oenology. Experience the entire winemaking journey From Soil to Bottle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/477131265f9ccd64d2f5f1e2e9b49f61.webp?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=59 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/253ddb7db46f9d554a5bbd8ca23b61c8.poster.avif?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/253ddb7db46f9d554a5bbd8ca23b61c8.webm?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/253ddb7db46f9d554a5bbd8ca23b61c8.mp4?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embrace the freedom to experiment and explore, as there's no fixed formula for crafting the perfect wine. Just like in life, there's no exact correct answer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/5fa7a5d55e7723c604ae439308150fba.webp?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=59 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/d83c2f617ef6c9e2ed344e13f4f31559.poster.avif?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/d83c2f617ef6c9e2ed344e13f4f31559.webm?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/d83c2f617ef6c9e2ed344e13f4f31559.mp4?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover the joy of blending different grape varieties, mastering the art of balance and complexity. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/5b8ca2c8ce56d91ddc2552777c0fc4e1.webp?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=59 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/58ac03c5080fc061fc8ad5bfb1f7cb73.poster.avif?t=1761870378\" width=614 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/58ac03c5080fc061fc8ad5bfb1f7cb73.webm?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873190/extras/58ac03c5080fc061fc8ad5bfb1f7cb73.mp4?t=1761870378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Navigate the challenges of the winemaking world, from unpredictable weather to demanding clients, as you strive to build your winery's reputation and success.",
